                <p>The Department of Economics, Jadavpur University, is recognised nationwide for its excellence in teaching and prospective research activities. Prof. Amartya Sen, the noted Welfare Economist and Nobel Laureate began his career here, as a teacher and a research scholar. Established in the year 1956, the department has consistently impressed the University Grants Commission with its teaching and research activities in various fields of economics. In 2005, the Department became the 4th Centre of Advanced Studies (CAS) in Economics in India.</p>
